<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA91">
<l>ūṉak kurampaiyi ṉuḷpuk kiruṇīkki</l>
<l>ñāṉac cuṭarkoḷīi nāṭōṟu – mēṉat</l>
<l>turuvā yulakiṭanta vūḻiyāṉ pāta</l>
<l>maruvātārk kuṇṭāmō vāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He of the aeons who entered into covers of flesh, dispelled</l>
<l>the darkness, kindled the flame of cognition every day,</l>
<l>who in the form of a boar dug out the world, is it that there is</l>
<l>heaven [even] for those who don’t join [his] feet?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
